  "texts": [
    "After RNA removal, padlock probes were hybridized to cDNA and circularized, followed by rolling circle amplification (RCA) to create rolonies.",
    "Rolonies were further crosslinked to the gel.",
    "b Imaging DART-FISH samples.",
    "Samples went through anchor round imaging followed by decoding rounds.",
    "In anchor round imaging, fluorescent probes complementary to the universal sequence and the 5' cDNA handle, present on all cDNA molecules, were hybridized at room temperature to visualize the distribution of rolonies and the shape of the somas (RiboSoma), respectively."
